value.name: Emirati student killed by Ohio police officer shot 5 times
value.description: The Summit County Medical Examiner said Tuesday 26-year-old Saif Nasser Mubarak Alameri was shot once in the head, once in the face and three times in the left leg by Hudson police officer Ryan Doran.
